On Wednesday, 18th March, 2026, Nima Forouzandeh Shahraki successfully defended his PhD thesis at TU Delft.

Nima’s PhD thesis is entitled Modelling Daylight for Existing Indoor Spaces - Towards formalisation and automation of input data for robust simulations.

Congratulations, Dr. Nima Forouzandeh Shahraki 🎉


